node.text: In honor of Breast Cancer Awareness month, we brought together breast cancer thrivers and healthcare heroes for a socially distanced shoot to share their stories. We put our paws up in honor of these inspiring women! We acknowledge there are many stories to tell and sadly many who aren’t here to tell theirs. Our campaign this month shares who YOU put your paws up in honor of and pays tribute to all those  impacted by breast cancer.

node.text: A few months ago, we launched “Magical Mary,” a Lilly Pulitzer & Make-a-Wish print with purpose created by our friend Mary and benefiting the Children’s Hospital of Philadelphia. We are happy to announce that due to high demand, we have restocked the girls popover and shift dress! Yes. Way. Shop now.
